  Author                   = {Jacka, Brendan and Applegate, Tanya and Poon, Art F and Raghwani, Jayna and Harrigan, P Richard and DeBeck, Kora and Milloy, M-J and Krajden, Mel and Olmstead, Andrea and Joy, Jeffrey B and Marshall, Brandon D L and Hayashi, Kanna and Pybus, Oliver G and Lima, Viviane Dias and Magiorkinis, Gkikas and Montaner, Julio and Lamoury, Francois and Dore, Gregory J and Wood, Evan and Grebely, Jason},
