  Month                    = {Jul},
  Note                     = {I conceived of and designed the study, developed the experimental system, performed all mutagenesis experiments, analyzed the data, and wrote the manuscript. This work has been described as ``a revolutionary set of experiments'' that were ``largely ahead of their time [and] address questions that are only now entering the mainstream'' [Curr Opin Struct Biol 26:104]},
